  (title_block
    (title "V-Cortex - USB Bridge e Auto-Programacao")
    (rev "v1.1")
    (company "V-Cortex")
    (comment 1 "Stage 2: CP2102N USB-UART + auto-prog via DTR/RTS + 2x BC817")
    (comment 2 "CRITICO: 100nF nos coletores BC817 para pulso de reset — sem isso ha reset loop")
    (comment 3 "EN e GPIO0 sao controlados pela sequencia DTR/RTS do esptool.py")
  )

  (lib_symbols)

  ;; ============================================================
  ;; CP2102N — USB-UART BRIDGE
  ;; ============================================================
  (text "U_USB — CP2102N-A02-GQFN28R\nLCSC: C6568 (Silicon Labs) — verificar disponibilidade\nAlternativa SOIC-28: CP2102-GMR (LCSC: buscar C2652)\nUSB Full-Speed 12Mbps, QFN-28 5x5mm\n\nPINAGEM PRINCIPAL (QFN-28):\n  pino 5  = VDD:   +3V3 alimentacao do CI\n  pino 6  = VBUS:  +5V do USB (detectacao de presenca)\n  pino 7  = REGIN: regulador interno -> cap C_REGIN(1uF) ao GND\n             (OU conectar REGIN ao +3V3 externo para bypass do regulador interno)\n  pino 8  = GND\n  pino 19 = GND\n  pino 24 = D+:   USB D+ (com ferrite ou 0Ohm serie, sem resistor de 22Ohm — CP2102N tem interno)\n  pino 25 = D-:   USB D- (idem D+)\n  pino 26 = TXD:  UART TX -> ESP32 RXD0 (GPIO3/RXD0)\n  pino 27 = RXD:  UART RX <- ESP32 TXD0 (GPIO1/TXD0)\n  pino 3  = RTS#: Request To Send (ativo LOW) -> Q3 BC817 -> EN ESP32\n  pino 4  = DTR#: Data Terminal Ready (ativo LOW) -> Q2 BC817 -> GPIO0 ESP32\n  pino 28 = GND (pad exposto)\n\nDECOUPLING CP2102N:\n  C_USB_VDD:  100nF X7R 0402 (LCSC: C14663) — bypass VDD pino5\n  C_USB_BULK: 10uF X5R 0805 (LCSC: C96446) — bulk VDD\n  C_REGIN:    1uF X5R 0402 (LCSC: C52923) — cap regulador interno REGIN pino7\n  C_VBUS:     10uF X5R 0805 (LCSC: C96446) — debounce VBUS pino6\n\nCONFIGURACAO VBUS:\n  +5V_USB -> [FB_USB ferrite 600Ohm] -> VBUS pino6\n  FB_USB: BLM21PG601SN1D (LCSC: C21179) — filtra ruido USB"
    (at 20 20)
    (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5)) (justify left top))
    (uuid "13000001-0000-0000-0000-000000000001")
  )

  ;; ============================================================
  ;; CIRCUITO AUTO-PROGRAMACAO — COM CAPACITORES 100nF (CORRIGIDO)
  ;; Engineering Guide secao 2.3 (era ausente o 100nF)
  ;; ============================================================
  (text "CIRCUITO AUTO-PROGRAMACAO ESP32\n(Engineering Guide secao 2.3 — com correcao do capacitor 100nF nos coletores)\n\nFUNCAO: programar ESP32 via USB sem pressionar botoes fisicos\nUsado automaticamente pelo esptool.py / arduino-cli\n\nCIRCUITO COMPLETO:\n\n  CP2102N                BC817 Q2               ESP32\n  DTR# ──[R_DTR 10k]──── Base Q2\n                          Coletor Q2 ──[C_DTR 100nF]──[R_GPIO0 10k]──[+3V3]\n                          Emissor Q2 ── GND                │\n                                                        GPIO0 (pino 25)\n\n  CP2102N                BC817 Q3               ESP32\n  RTS# ──[R_RTS 10k]──── Base Q3\n                          Coletor Q3 ──[C_RTS 100nF]──[R_EN 10k]──[+3V3]\n                          Emissor Q3 ── GND                │\n                                                        EN (pino 3)\n\n*** CRITICO: CAPACITORES C_DTR e C_RTS (100nF cada) ***\n  FUNCAO: criar pulso no EN sem manter o estado LOW continuamente\n  SEM eles: EN fica LOW enquanto RTS# esta ativo -> reset loop durante comunicacao\n  COM eles: transitorio de reset (~1ms) e EN volta para HIGH rapidamente\n  Diferenciador RC: tau = R_EN(10k) * C_RTS(100nF) = 1ms\n  Largura do pulso de reset: ~1ms -> suficiente para reset do ESP32\n\nCOMPONENTES:\n  Q2: BC817-40LT1G SOT-23 (LCSC: C22400355) — NPN, Ic=500mA, hFE=100-600\n  Q3: BC817-40LT1G SOT-23 (LCSC: C22400355) — mesmo tipo Q2\n  R_DTR: 10k 0402 (LCSC: C25741) — base Q2\n  R_RTS: 10k 0402 (LCSC: C25741) — base Q3\n  C_DTR: 100nF X7R 0402 (LCSC: C14663) — diferenciador GPIO0 (NOVO)\n  C_RTS: 100nF X7R 0402 (LCSC: C14663) — diferenciador EN (NOVO)\n\nSEQUENCIA ESPTOOL.PY (automatica):\n  1. DTR=HIGH, RTS=LOW: Q2 OFF (GPIO0 -> pull-up HIGH=normal), Q3 ON (EN -> LOW=reset transitorio)\n  2. DTR=LOW, RTS=HIGH: Q3 OFF (EN -> HIGH via R_EN), Q2 ON (GPIO0 -> LOW=download mode)\n  3. ESP32 sobe em Download Mode, esptool flasha o firmware\n  4. DTR=HIGH, RTS=HIGH: ambos OFF -> ESP32 boot normal"
    (at 20 300)
    (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5)) (justify left top))
    (uuid "13000002-0000-0000-0000-000000000001")
  )

  ;; ============================================================
  ;; CONECTOR USB
  ;; ============================================================
  (text "CONECTOR USB — J_USB:\n\nOPCAO RECOMENDADA: USB Micro-B SMD\n  LCSC: C10418 (Amphenol) ou C168688 (HRO)\n  Mais robusto mecanicamente em ambiente automotivo (vibracoes)\n\nOPCAO ALTERNATIVA: USB-C 2.0 SMD\n  LCSC: C2765186 ou C165948\n  Requer R_CC1=5.1k e R_CC2=5.1k ao GND (modo UFP device)\n\nPINAGEM USB MICRO-B:\n  pino 1 (VBUS): +5V -> [FB_USB] -> VBUS CP2102N + C_VBUS(10uF) ao GND\n  pino 2 (D-):   direto ao D- CP2102N\n  pino 3 (D+):   direto ao D+ CP2102N\n  pino 4 (ID):   NC\n  pino 5 (GND):  GND\n  Shield:        GND via capacitor 1nF/100V (LCSC: C14858)\n\nSE USB-C:\n  R_CC1: 5.1k 0402 (LCSC: C23186) — CC1 -> GND (identifica device/UFP)\n  R_CC2: 5.1k 0402 (LCSC: C23186) — CC2 -> GND\n  Sem pull-ups: dispositivo nao anuncia fast-charging"
    (at 600 20)
    (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5)) (justify left top))
    (uuid "13000003-0000-0000-0000-000000000001")
  )

  ;; ============================================================
  ;; RESUMO BOM — STAGE 2 (USB)
  ;; ============================================================
  (text "RESUMO BOM — STAGE 2 (USB e Auto-programacao)\n\nREF           VALUE           LCSC         FUNCAO\nU_USB         CP2102N QFN28   C6568        USB-UART bridge\nC_USB_VDD     100nF           C14663       Bypass VDD CP2102N\nC_USB_BULK    10uF            C96446       Bulk VDD CP2102N\nC_REGIN       1uF             C52923       Cap regulador interno REGIN\nC_VBUS        10uF            C96446       Debounce VBUS USB\nFB_USB        BLM21PG601SN1   C21179       Ferrite VBUS USB\nQ2            BC817-40LT1G    C22400355    NPN auto-prog DTR -> GPIO0\nQ3            BC817-40LT1G    C22400355    NPN auto-prog RTS -> EN\nR_DTR         10k             C25741       Base Q2\nR_RTS         10k             C25741       Base Q3\nC_DTR         100nF           C14663       NOVO: diferenciador pulso GPIO0\nC_RTS         100nF           C14663       NOVO: diferenciador pulso EN\nJ_USB         USB Micro-B SMD C10418       Conector USB programacao"
    (at 600 300)
    (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5)) (justify left top))
    (uuid "13000004-0000-0000-0000-000000000001")
  )

